snippet.title: RogueClick Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the trailer for an incremental RPG called "RogueClick," out now on Steam, Google Play, and itch.io!

RogueClick Webpage: https://chrysolite.software/rogueclick
Get it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1908900/RogueClick/
Get it on Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=software.chrysolite.rogueclick
Get it on itch.io: https://chrysolite-software.itch.io/rogueclick

Music:
Crusade Heavy Industry by Kevin MacLeod
Link: https://incompetech.filmmusic.io/song/4678-crusade-heavy-industry
License: https://filmmusic.io/standard-license
